CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FWords by Health and Science Producer
OL,8,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,10,FExperts are warning that the UK is
OL,11,Ffalling behind in its bid to protect
OL,12,Ffirefighters from exposure to forever
OL,13,Fchemicals.
OL,15,FAlso known as PFAS, forever chemicals
OL,16,Fare a group of around 15,000 man-made
OL,17,Fchemicals which can take hundreds or
OL,18,Fthousands of years to break down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FOne use of PFAS was in AFFF -
OL,8,Ffirefighting foams used to put out
OL,9,Fliquid-fuel fires like those caused by
OL,10,Fburning petrol or diesel.
OL,12,FThe foam was highly effective but some
OL,13,Fcontained PFOA, a forever chemical
OL,14,Fthat is linked to kidney and
OL,15,Ftesticular cancer, amongst other
OL,16,Fchemicals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FWayne Crossman was a firefighter in
OL,8,F2005. He remembers using the foam at
OL,9,Fthe site of the Buncefield fire in
OL,10,F2005 ` a major fire at an oil storage
OL,11,Ffacility in Hertfordshire which took
OL,12,Ffive days to put out.
OL,14,F"During that whole incident I never
OL,15,Fwore a mask. I don't believe I ever
OL,16,Fsee anyone in breathing apparatus
OL,17,Feither," Wayne said. He also said they
OL,18,Fused lots of the foam in training
OL,19,Fexercises.
OL,21,FNow he has leukaemia.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FAlthough the link between blood cancer
OL,8,Fand PFAS has not been proven, Wayne
OL,9,Fbelieves exposure to chemicals during
OL,10,Fhis time as a firefighter could have
OL,11,Fcontributed.
OL,13,F"It was always thought that you risk
OL,14,Fyour life in fire. It was always
OL,15,Fthought that that was our ultimate
OL,16,Fdanger, where in fact cancer in the
OL,17,Fbrigade is killing much more."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FIn July 2025, the government banned
OL,8,FAFFF foams containing PFOA. Phased
OL,9,Fbans for other foams containing PFAS
OL,10,Fwill come in gradually, with a total
OL,11,Fban expected by 2030.
OL,13,FFire services are all transitioning
OL,14,Ftowards Fluorine-free foams, but there
OL,15,Fare concerns that firefighters are
OL,16,Fstill being exposed to other types of
OL,17,FPFAS - some of which, it is feared,
OL,18,Fmay be harmful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FIn 2024, the Fire Brigades Union (FBU)
OL,8,Fwarned of the "quadruple threat" faced
OL,9,Fby firefighters of PFAS exposure in
OL,10,Ffirefighting foam, fires, fire sites
OL,11,Fand fire stations, and both in and on
OL,12,Ftheir protective equipment.
OL,14,F"PFAS used to exist in the
OL,15,Ffirefighting foam we used in great
OL,16,Fquantities, it exists in PPE and it
OL,17,Fwill also exist in other firefighting
OL,18,Fequipment," says Adam Taylor, National
OL,19,FOfficer at the FBU.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,F"We want studies done to help
OL,8,Feradicate PFAS from the firefighting
OL,9,Fservice, ultimately making our members
OL,10,Fand firefighting safer."
OL,12,FIn addition to PFAS, firefighters face
OL,13,Fa number of other exposure risks.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FA report released in February by the
OL,8,FLondon Assembly Fire Committee found
OL,9,Fthat firefighters in London may be
OL,10,Froutinely exposed to a number of other
OL,11,Ftoxic substances including asbestos,
OL,12,Fheavy metals and persistent organic
OL,13,Fpollutants.
OL,15,FAnna Stec, a professor in Fire
OL,16,FChemistry and Toxicity at the
OL,17,FUniversity of Lancashire, said: "The
OL,18,Ffirefighter occupation has been
OL,19,Fclassified as carcinogenic by the
OL,20,FWorld Health Organisation.
OL,26,@yD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,F"We have also got many countries not
OL,8,Fonly providing presumptive law and
OL,9,Frecognising occupational cancer but
OL,10,Falso offering health monitoring.
OL,12,F"In the UK, currently, the
OL,13,Ffirefighting occupation is not
OL,14,Fclassified as carcinogenic due to lack
OL,15,Fof data."
OL,17,FShe has been commissioned by the Fire
OL,18,FBrigades Union to study the impacts of
OL,19,FPFAS exposure on firefighters.
OL,26,@wD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,F"From the epidemiological and
OL,8,Ftoxicological evidence, we know that
OL,9,FPFAS are associated with a number of
OL,10,Femerging health disorders. What is
OL,11,Freally needed is to establish UK
OL,12,Fsafety threshold limits for PFAS in
OL,13,Fthe blood" she says.
OL,15,FThe UK and EU have taken differing
OL,16,Fapproaches to dealing with the threat
OL,17,Fof PFAS exposure.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FThe EU is implementing a broad,
OL,8,Fprecautionary ban on all PFAS
OL,9,Fchemicals in firefighting foams by
OL,10,F2030.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the UK is targeting
OL,13,Fspecific harmful substances like PFOA,
OL,14,Fmeaning manufacturing companies can
OL,15,Fswap one chemical for another, known
OL,16,Fas 'regrettable substitution.'
OL,18,FProfessor Stec is worried this could
OL,19,Flead to further problems in the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,F"By the time we have got a
OL,8,Frecommendation to ban and phase out
OL,9,Fone of the chemicals, we have already
OL,10,Freplaced it with another one that we
OL,11,Fthen find out is from the same group
OL,12,Fand poses the same health threats,"
OL,13,Fshe said.
OL,15,F"But because of lack of data, it will
OL,16,Ftake another decade to phase the new
OL,17,Fchemical out and ban it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FIt is a concern echoed by the Chair of
OL,8,Fthe Environmental Audit Committee,
OL,9,FToby Perkins MP. The committee has an
OL,10,Fongoing inquiry into the impacts of
OL,11,Fforever chemicals.
OL,13,F"I think it's important that we have
OL,14,Fconsistency with the rest of Europe. I
OL,15,Fthink it's important that we have a
OL,16,Fplan for legacy PFAS and a plan for
OL,17,Freducing future contamination,"
OL,18,FPerkins said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774440171
OL,3,CCalls for stronger PFAS regulations
OL,4,Camid rising cancer concerns in
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,F"I think we need a regime in place
OL,8,Fthat adopts the polluter pays
OL,9,Fprinciple.
OL,11,F"And I think we need a regime in place
OL,12,Fthat adopts the precautionary
OL,13,Fprinciple which means that until we
OL,14,Fare certain that they are safe, we're
OL,15,Fnot allowing them, rather than a
OL,16,Fsituation that has been described to
OL,17,Fus as whack-a-mole where every time
OL,18,Fyou rule out one kind of compound, you
OL,19,Ffind a marginally different one
OL,20,Freturning."
OL,26,@oD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
